	<plot>Bust the video game speed barrier wide open with Sonic the Hedgehog. Blaze by in a blur using the Super Sonic Spin Attack. Plummet down tunnels and spin through space. Bounce around till you're dizzy in a pinball machine. You've never seen anything like it!Cheat: Passing a wallIn the second act of the Green Hill zone, after the pit of water, there is a spring.  Hit the spring and jump so you hit the corner of the wall. if done corect, sonic will get stuck on the wall and if you jump to the right, sonic can go to the nearest place above him (the waterfall leading to the chaos emerald) Cheat: Unlock hidden endingBy finding and obtaining the six Chaos Emeralds hidden throughout each zone and completing the game, you get to watch the true, better ending sequence.</plot>
